overview: Tomomi, who started a part-time job at a convenience store, was confused by her senior, Sugiura. Taking advantage of Tomomi's obedient personality, she steals the eyes of the other clerks and engages in sexual harassment. She was threatened that "If she doesn't come to work, I will rush to her house", and the night she entered the night shift alone with Sugiura without being able to consult anyone. Tomomi is finally raped by Sugiura...
title: Target List.11 Tachibana Hina
